EDIT: I have remade this map for DoD:S, It now looks MUCH, MUCH better, please check it out if you have DoD:S!!
aim_dday by Jora Hill AKA "Rusty9k" is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-Noncommercial-No Derivative Works 3.0 New Zealand License. Based on "Point Du Hoc." and Call of Duty 2's American campaign. An older version of this map was uploaded to garrysmod.org Map will have problems with bots, there is no nav file and the bots will not be able to use ladders, you can still play with bots but they will usually just stay on their side of the cliff. Basically the CT's spawn in the boats and have to make their way up the rope ladders, the T's have to defend the cliff from the bunkers ect.. You can find a video of an old version of this map here http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eMIzgHGnkVA This version has more bunkers and places to hide, its just better overall :). I made this map quite a long time ago, I've gotten alot better at mapping now, so there might be a version 2 if this map gets downloaded here enough, I will add a 3dskybox and posibly more land at the back of the cliff with more defences for the germ.. I mean Terrorists :P Thanks for downloading! If you want to make any movies or redistrube the map somewhere or whatver, PLEASE Contact me @ jorahill@hotmail.com Thanks. - Rusty
